<h2>Sign up!</h2>

<p>
  You may submit up to 5 pieces of poetry or one work of short prose. We enjoy a wide range of styles and genresâ€”what we want most are pieces that demonstrate a clear voice, unafraid to be passionate and reveling in sound.
</p>
<p>
  You need to have an account with us to contribute.  Please sign up below.  
  After you submit this form, we'll send you a note to confirm your email address, 
  and then you can log in.
</p>

<% form_for :user, @user || User.new, :url => users_path do |f| -%>

<div>
  <%= f.label :email %>
  <br/>
  <%= f.text_field :email, :class => "text" %>
  <%= f.error_message_on :email %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.label :password %>
  <br/>
  <%= f.password_field :password, :class => "text" %>
  <%= f.error_message_on :password %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.label :password_confirmation, "Confirm Password" %>
  <br/>
  <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :class => "text" %>
  <%= f.error_message_on :password_confirmation %>
</div>

<p><%= submit_tag 'Sign up', :class => "button" %></p>
<% end -%>
